  <h1>Quick Start</h1>

  <p>
    Get a design system health report in under 2 minutes.
  </p>

  <h2>Interactive Setup (Recommended)</h2>

  <p>The easiest way to get started is with the interactive wizard:</p>

  <pre><code>npx ahoybuoy dock</code></pre>

  <p>
    This runs a scan, shows your results, and guides you through configuration.
    <a href="/docs/cli/dock">Learn more about buoy dock</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>Step 1: Run a Drift Scan</h2>

  <p>From your project root, run:</p>

  <pre><code>npx ahoybuoy drift</code></pre>

